1. Main Page 1
    - press “Pair with Keyboard” -> check bluetooth signal from Edison and connect the edison.
2. Main Page 2
    - press “Disconnect” -> disconnect Edison
3. Customize Key Button Screen
    - Play Sound -> look for the audio file for the specific button and play it
    - Select Custom Sound -> look for the audio file folder in the Edison and show the filenames
    - Set Quiet Hours -> take an input for the desired time and set quiet hours for the keyboard.
4. Statistics Screen
    - Export Data -> Convert the file received from Edison to .csv format. Send the converted file to the written email.
    - (Optional) Show chart based on the file from Edison
5. Setting Screen
    - Disable Keyboard -> disable sounds, stop counting
